            <div class="col-xs-12">
                <div class="description"><h1>WATERSCHOOLS</h1>

<h2>Water is vital. If there is no water, there is no life.</h2>

<p>Ample water consumption is absolutely necessary for maintaining optimal health and brain function. People usually meet their fluid needs by drinking when thirsty. But specially in schools, there is always a lot going on. That´s why pupils often forget to drink, even when they feel thirsty.</p>

<p>This is where the Erasmus+ project "WATERSCHOOLS" comes in. Pupils/students should be encouraged to drink enough healthy tap water in their everyday life at school.</p>
